title: Japanese Food
description: Food was good and very tasty! Affordable mentaiko Japanese food, the mentaiko fries were good and the spicy mentaiko was not too spicy or salty. Very nice meal

title: for all Mentaiko lovers!
description: Super affordable Mentaiko place! I had the Mentaiko salmon and spicy Mentaiko soft shell crab. They were so generous with their portions of salmon and mentaiko! It was also my first time trying soft shell crab with spicy mentaiko, it was interesting :)

title: One of the Most Affordable & Tasty Japanese Food @ Tampines
description: Ordered Spicy Mentai Chicken bowl and Mentai Salmon bowl, both under the price of $10. I have to say, it's definitely worth the amount spent. The chicken and salmon were really fresh! If you're concerned with the spice level of the spicy mentaiko sauce, be rest assured that there is a kick of spice, but definitely not too spicy. The amount of mentaiko sauce and portion of the meal provided was so generous and service was great! Looking forward to recommend this place to my friends and family. :)

title: Good and Affordable
description: Great place to satisfy mentaiko cravings, very affordable. Had the mentaiko salmon and spicy mentaiko fried chicken. Mentaiko mayo was really good and the heat in the spicy mentaiko made it better.

title: BEST MENTAI DISH IN THE EAST
description: Never would have expect such great tasting mentai dish in a coffeeshop! The spicy or regular mentai is both great and the meats tasted great when paired with the mentaiko! 100% I'll be a returning customer (especially when its so near me! Yay!)

title: Mentai-YES
description: I can’t believe the mentaiko here is so good!! I love how the perfectly fried chicken goes with mentaiko - this is heaven in a bite. You can’t find this quality at this price point anywhere else, highly recommend!

title: Great Value Mentai Don!
description: Absolutely loved the thick and creamy spicy mentaiko sauce they have here! Really recommend trying out the Spicy Salmon Mentai!!

title: Great value and tasty food!
description: Great value and tasty food! I had the unagi tama don and the mentaiko soft shell crab but i forgot to take a pic of that one. I'm gonna get the salmon next time I'm in the east!

title: Mentaiko Supreme
description: Good food good service good mentaiko. Ordered spicy salmon mentaiko Don and soft shell crab w mentaiko

title: Hearty Meal
description: Located at a relatively new neighbourhood. Menu is interesting, especially for Mentai lovers. Do check out this place!

title: Affordable Rice Bowls
description: Unique dishes in a neighbourhood setting. Got the soft shell crab and unagi bowl. There is a variety of other side dishes as well!

title: Mentaiko!!
description: Love the flavour of the mentaiko here - sweet and tangy! Had the spicy salmon and mentaiko fries. The spicy salmon comes with the right level for spice for spice lovers and also the portion of the salmon cutlet is very value for money!
